horoscopes: ['Beware of false friends.','A journey of a thousand miles begins with a single step.','Your lucky numbers are 7, 9, and 23.','The best things in life are worth waiting for.','You will soon receive unexpected news.','Everything happens for a reason.','Your hard work will soon pay off.','Love is right around the corner.','You will soon discover a hidden talent.','Good things come to those who wait.','A change is coming, embrace it.','Believe in yourself and others will too.']
